<br>
1) Self cast blade turn. Tired as hell of being revealed by greys hitting for 0 damage.<br>
<br>
2) Self cast Magic turn, tired of AE spells easily revealing us. Especially since now every one and their dog has an ae spell it seems.<br>
<br>
3) For the shadow blade escape spell, would like this. Instant cast spell that makes 3 clones of us and teleports us and the clones each in a random compass point direction. Range would be 100 per ten levls from the casters spot the clones would then run for 5 seconds then poof. This spell would have to break /stick and drop us all who have us targeted.<br>
      Things that would balance this spell is the range is not all that great. The fact it could send you into agro mobs or even closer to the enemy lines. While it would allow you to escape those beating on you no guarante it will put you in a better spot.<br>
