<br>
1) find a place where the time it would take the monster to get to me was long (for instance throwing dagger at an opponent that had to run up a set of stairs to get to me) and then I would hide and wait for the monster to arrive.<br>
<br>
2) I would throw a dagger and then run until hide was available, then I would hide and wait for monster.<br>
<br>
Neither of these options are available now since damage breaks stealth and the monsters always hit me first.<br>
<br>
I think we should be able to poison the daggers, the damage would still be tiny, the range would still be tiny, but we could at least pull for our group.  Nightshades and Infiltaratos can do this with crossbows/spells.<br>
<br>
Throwing daggers would actually be a lot of fun if we could poison them, we could use them in keep defense, we could use them to hit running enemy.<br>
<br>
They do squat for damage.  I have probably thrown about 300 of them, maybe more, and I would say the most damage I ever did was around 10 points.  At least if they were poisoned we could do something with them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ufandangodarkdance.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fandango Darkdance</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/13/02 5:24:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2152.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: First Revision of the SHADOWBLADE report</span><hr size=1> Only use I have found for daggers is to break the mez of monsters. Had some people kill stealing so we stopped pulling, made a drink. Came back and watched, they finally got a bad pull a mob aggroed the puller so now they had 3 and only a group of two players. Healer mezd I through my dagger broke the mez both died I laughed and we went back to hunting as our healer did jigs on them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=2152.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=2152.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2152.topic&index=14><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=2152.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email Thi